subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution . Tropical and subtropical regions worldwide, occasionally boreal; in the southern hemisphere to 50°S (
Vinogradov et al . 1996
). In the eastern Pacific it ranges from Newport to Baja California (García Madrigal 2007), in the Gulf of California ( Siegel-Causey 1982 ; present study), and southward to Panama and Ecuador ( Guillén Pozo 2007 ,
Valencia et al . 2013
).
